<item>
            <title>[SPARK-17027] PolynomialExpansion.choose is prone to integer overflow </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-17027</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current implementation computes power of k directly and because of that it is susceptible to integer overflow on relatively small input (4 features, degree equal 10).  It would be better to use recursive formula instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
